Title: Sur Moi

I've done a few things I'm proud of.

  • Built a web application for the City of Flint to keep records of lead service line replacements, which led to published research, and the founding of BlueConduit.

  • Part of the early engineering team at Urbint, which grew from around 20 heads to 70 during the few years I was there. What a ride.

These days I'm taking it easy, working part time, reading and learning more musical instruments and styles.
